measure.CatchLine: Establishes Oregon Right to Rest Act.
measure.MeasureSummary: Establishes Oregon Right to Rest Act. Makes violation unlawful practice enforceable by Commissioner of Bureau of Labor and Industries or by civil action.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to rights of persons experiencing homelessness; creating new provisions; and amending ORS 659A.885.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to rights of persons experiencing homelessness.
measure.FiscalImpact: May have fiscal impact, but no statement yet issued
measure.RevenueImpact: May have revenue impact, but no statement yet issued

historyActions.ActionText: First reading. Referred to Speaker's desk.
